active.name: Dragons Alliance
active.desc: The most dangerous neutral guild. Respect to be respected. Old days of Dolera

active.name: Order of the Dragon
active.desc: Guild Leader Ozmerino Nolofinwe Pallanen with the Guild Banner & the weary guildsfolk of The Order of The Dragon standing on upon yet another hilltop looking across yet another valley of new adventures. With sadness perhaps of this time of change and the passing yet again of fallen friends. This new adventure in a new world with a new beginning. While yet the Banner stands the goodfolk raise a glass of mead beneath the mistletoe.
